    <h1 class="mb-4">Report Generation</h1>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Generate Comprehensive Report</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Generate a detailed report containing:
                <ul>
                    <li>Plant Popularity Statistics</li>
                    <li>Category Statistics</li>
                    <li>User Information</li>
                    <li>Action Frequencies</li>
